d8c1bd083a144f5332871572b17b05b63","tid":279302,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T17:10:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56192997732fc0db4845da332610afc25d18958","tid":279302,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T22:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n受邀出席第28屆台灣金曲獎嘅 容祖兒 Joey Yung，喺現場透露咗而家<span style=\"color: red;\">已經籌備緊2017全新國語專輯</span>喇！😍<br />\n#第28屆金曲獎<br />\n#容祖兒2017全新國語專輯 <br />\n#密切期待<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19400029_1266605843438353_8039732908117471745_n.jpg?oh=87ba583122989c0d38c41e96b410a5fb&amp;oe=59E1EFE2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19400029_1266605843438353_8039732908117471745_n.jpg%3Foh%3D87ba583122989c0d38c41e96b410a5fb%26oe%3D59E1EFE2&h=4531283a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19399734_1266605866771684_3477095634348604379_n.jpg?oh=964ebc447ebdf6a161e20ecad099e548&amp;oe=59D4051C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19399734_1266605866771684_3477095634348604379_n.jpg%3Foh%3D964ebc447ebdf6a161e20ecad099e548%26oe%3D59D4051C&h=25d0a1a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f42d7cfc60221723b55e7db248fe1d3e65586037","tid":279302,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"金曲獎：容祖兒預告將出國語專輯<br />\n<br />\n台灣第28屆金曲獎頒獎典禮今晚於台北小巨蛋舉行，擔任頒獎嘉賓的天后容祖兒以一身半透視長裙現身行星光大道，主持大讚她的歌《黃昏點唱機》好聽，祖兒即說：「有品味！」問到音樂計劃？她透露將推出國語專輯：「昨天來到就開會，下個Project就是出國語專輯，希望年底前趕得及出，7-8月會在台灣錄音。」又指已與同事講好這次的宣傳要做得好，所以屆時會在台灣留一段較長的時間，希望歌迷及傳媒感受到她的誠意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170624/bkn-20170624185517816-0624_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170624%2Fbkn-20170624185517816-0624_00862_001.html&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3c7bd9e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170624/bkn-20170624185517816-0624_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次唔得既就安心去做劉太啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a7ecde8d06fdc60e2ebad6d4e1c5d410455c4c","tid":279302,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d5fcbb66a4b22545222cc9841f1ace445af4a9","tid":279302,"uid":20665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd9e5b6d262119c3596c5ab356f146d679661a3","tid":279302,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T18:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4314e50c83bfcbac4279a778fbe4ce2331eac6","tid":279302,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"最好時光 @ 二十周年文藝晚會 (Credit: jylover@JFF)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aeThmjm6xx0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaeThmjm6xx0&d=n56Gtz%2FeaVfJwK%2Fd5Uq8XEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=eb45f545\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aeThmjm6xx0</a>"},{"pid":"804b1f28aadf00892b88462aff3fe46e9cd7d41e","tid":279302,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好時光 @ 二十周年文藝晚會 (Credit: jylover@JFF)<br />\n<br />\n<img src